### Skapar en bok
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "author": "Robert Martin",
  "isbn": "9780132350884",
  "publishedYear": 2008
}

### Hämtar alla böcker
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books

### Hämtar en bok med id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/1